text: Kamila Zakirova (born 25 December 1992) is a Kazakhstani female water polo player. She competed for the Kazakhstan women's national water polo team in the 2015 World Aquatics Championships. 2017 World Aquatics Championships, and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * water-polo-reports-women-day-2 fina.org * water-polo-reports-women-day-1 fina.org Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani water polo players
